 * Semantic Bootstrap only; the chart reads --bs-* tokens so it tracks the theme + skin.
 *
 * Empty/unavailable-data is a first-class state, not an error: the client renders a full ZEROED
 * scaffold (0 tiles, a flat chart over the window, "No data yet" tables) and shows a calm INFO
 * note — a fresh GA4 property with no traffic should look intentional, never a red failure.
 */
